{"tid":131320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反擊了!]警一連5日行動！打撃公共車輛司機用手機無戴安全帶","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T06:30:58.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35430b031a0befe726a0ba0e9d7ee0e42dc571a1","tid":131320,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"警方今日（23/2）起至2月27日進行為期5日的全港公共服務車輛（包括的士、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">專營公共巴士</span></span>、公共小巴、私家小巴及私家學童小巴）安全執法行動，打擊違例行為，包括司機在駕駛時使用流動通訊設備、超速駕駛及與安全帶相關的罪行等。有關道路安全資訊，可瀏覽警隊網頁： <a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/05_traffic_matters/enforcement.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F05_traffic_matters%2Fenforcement.html&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=72b213fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/05_traffic_matters/enforcement.html</a>。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲公共服務車輛司機駕駛時切勿使用流動通訊設備，及須遵守道路交通規例，留意路面情況，配戴安全帶並提醒乘客配戴安全帶。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方數字，去年涉及公共服務車輛的交通意外有6,803宗，佔整體交通意外數字的42%，導致9,210人傷亡，當中48人死亡。警方發言人表示，這些交通意外主要成因是司機駕駛時不留神、跟車太貼、胡亂轉線、沒有確保乘客的安全，及不適當地或不合法地轉向。"},{"pid":"2fc167a3920f7ba759c7b5eb9ba34b0506926657","tid":131320,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"籌旗幫班監躉"},{"pid":"f134e245a4468618e767ac3cd67b805e901cd7d8","tid":131320,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"包唔包括潮聯嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923fb17d2d859270e474ec488ddbba28ead83ec3","tid":131320,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"我好撚驚呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"46932bbf9750f67f4ad77dc9e10c795bf14b39ac","tid":131320,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"阿sir：屌，邊間小巴公司唔交片，就掃鳩佢場。見一架掃一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br